                option_label: 'C',
                option_text: 'LinkedIn did not invest enough in onboarding users to the Stories format, so adoption was slow because people did not know how to use the feature.',
                quality: 'surface',
                points: 1,
                competencies: ['product_design'],
                explanation: 'Onboarding quality is an execution problem; even with perfect onboarding, a professional who understands Stories perfectly would still weigh the reputational risk before posting casual, ephemeral content to their professional network.',
